snippet.title: Is Obama Too Weak To Handle Jihadi John?

localized.description: Intelligence agencies are on the hunt for Jihadi John, the English rapper who murdered James Foley. Voice recognition points to a Londoner, 23 year old Abdel-Majed Abdel Bary. What's Britian doing about it? Is Obama strong enough of a leader to fight these guys? After hearing about the event he went and played golf. Is he disengaged about what's going on? Tell everyone what you think.
